action.description: Passed Second Reading as amended in HD 1; placed on the calendar for Third Reading with Representative(s) Alcos, Amato, Souza voting aye with reservations; Representative(s) Garcia, Matsumoto, Muraoka, Reyes Oda, Shimizu voting no (5) and Representative(s) Cochran, Pierick, Templo, Ward excused (4).
